name: 1 | Welcome to chulitoslove
description:
He call me Mamichula and automatically makes me laugh, I call him Papichulo to play along but certainly says it with more attitude. So, he is chulito and I am chulita. Together we are chulitoslove. 

Welcome to this place! 

Take my hand and enter our world; get excited, get inspired, get angry, fall in love, dream, cry... Feel and identify yourself with my anecdotes and our love story.
